{"type": "article", "id": 9126, "title": "Valentina Pink 香水", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-04T07:50:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235220rfO3tmhjXDIBcUEp.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tValentino 最近推出了一款叫做 Valentina Pink 的新香水。香水主调为新鲜的牡丹和玫瑰花香，搭配了前调的草莓、麝香、琥珀、喀什米尔木和杏桃糖香，再加上粉嫩的配色和花朵形状的外观设计，营造出浓郁的恋爱气息。<a href=\"http://shop.nordstrom.com/c/valentino-perfume-for-women?cm_ven=Linkshare&amp;cm_cat=partner&amp;cm_pla=10&amp;cm_ite=1&amp;siteId=Jv.v1_Wldzg-BTaFRKGbOWaQCwr59X9NbQ\" target=\"_blank\">可以关注 Nordstorm 购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052352188GtlSXw9NvC5bEo1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.21038251\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235218XWhf4CVuqYUimw2a.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235219A4yhvcqDTkgpdnW6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.02037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}